OL,3,CExplosion at military weapons factory
OL,5,FFire crews were called to the scene of
OL,6,Fan explosion at a site belonging to
OL,7,FBAE Systems, Britain's biggest defence
OL,8,Ffirm.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,11,Fsaid the incident happened at the BAE
OL,12,Fbase in Glascoed, Monmouthshire, at
OL,13,Faround 10.49am on Wednesday, 17 April.
OL,15,FIn a tweet on X, the fire service said
OL,16,Fan "incident control post has been set
OL,17,Fup to deal with the incident".
