OL,3,CExplosion at military weapons factory
OL,5,F"The explosion did not cause any
OL,6,Finjuries, evacuation procedures were
OL,7,Fimmediately instigated and everything
OL,8,Fwas thoroughly checked.
OL,10,F"I am told there is always a small
OL,11,Frisk involved in this particular
OL,12,Foperation, which is exactly why it is
OL,13,Fcarried out with remote control in a
OL,14,Frestricted area of the site. There
OL,15,Fwere no risks to any members of the
OL,16,Fpublic."
